{"tid":1531850,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"外國人焗住用google translate都要上連登，究竟幾時先肯開英文台/英文interface (2)","createTime":"2019-09-02T10:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:40:46.000Z","uid":34154,"like":90,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"c6efd6bd8d7ab0cc90a1f11373571ba8da6c1176","tid":1531850,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:54:19.000Z","msg":"原post1001咗:外國人焗住用google translate都要上連登，究竟幾時先肯開英文台/英文interface<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530310</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y6JtQBP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY6JtQBP.png&h=61d9f138&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/EnzoMazak/status/1167912756592295941?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEnzoMazak%2Fstatus%2F1167912756592295941%3Fs%3D19&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR22WjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=19ee538a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEnzoMazak%2Fstatus%2F1167912756592295941%3Fs%3D19&h=bc33fb5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/EnzoMazak/status/1167912756592295941?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n我要求連仔：<br />\n1. 設計英文interface，比外國人可以用英文navigate 連登<br />\n2. 開英文台，只許用英文討論<br />\n<br />\n理由<br />\n1. 連登國際出左名，有外國人想黎睇<br />\n2. 可以提供第一手行動資訊比外國傳媒，唔洗再比scmp壟斷<br />\n3. 連登可藉此機會expand到一個新層次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當連登仔開始瘋用twitter接觸國際，連登又點可以故步自封"},{"pid":"fd8868a34676579f20e0a8ddec54f3f39200c231","tid":1531850,"uid":88263,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:57:27.000Z","msg":"支持開英文台/英文版/國際台<br />\n<br />\n我平時Share 文宣都係Share 英文多人For 外國朋友<br />\n<br />\n我自己啲朋友政見都差唔多，唔洗再傳中文"},{"pid":"3482de37b890c48f1355309ccb01756f21b483fc","tid":1531850,"uid":119458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" clas